  Ôćĺ(comp)Effector,ReceptorÔćĺ(ref)Interaction,Interface.
  **CASCADE**: all elements `DRAFT->ABANDONED` (terminal
  is in both aggregation, composition, and reference scope).

  SC-93 ÔÇö Structure(ACTIVE), Mechanism(ACTIVE),
  Effector(ACTIVE), Receptor(ACTIVE), Interaction(ACTIVE).
  New Mechanism2(DRAFT), Effector2(DRAFT), Receptor2(DRAFT).
  Structure `ACTIVE->SUSPENDED`.
  Mechanism(ACTIVE): **CASCADE** `ACTIVE->SUSPENDED`.
  Effector(ACTIVE): **CASCADE** `ACTIVE->SUSPENDED`.
  Receptor(ACTIVE): **CASCADE** `ACTIVE->SUSPENDED`.
  Interaction: **CASCADE** `ACTIVE->SUSPENDED` (via ref).
  Mechanism2(DRAFT): step 1 DRAFT Ôëá ACTIVE Ôćĺ **NO-OP**.
  Effector2(DRAFT): **NO-OP** (Mechanism2 not cascaded).
  Receptor2(DRAFT): **NO-OP** (Mechanism2 not cascaded).

  ====

  **┬ž11 ÔÇö Composition cascade failure blocks source**

  SC-95 ÔÇö Mechanism(ACTIVE), Effector(ACTIVE),
  Receptor(ACTIVE). Effector.Object(RETIRED),
  Receptor.Object(ACTIVE).
  Mechanism `ACTIVE->SUSPENDED`.
  Effector cascade step 2: Object RETIRED Ôłë
  {ACTIVE,SUSPENDED,DEPRECATED} Ôćĺ fails.
  **BLOCKED**: Mechanism `ACTIVE->SUSPENDED` MUST be
  rejected (composition ÔÇö on failure: reject source).

  SC-96 ÔÇö Mechanism(ACTIVE), Effector(ACTIVE),
  Receptor(ACTIVE). Effector.Object(ACTIVE),
  Receptor.Object(ABANDONED).
  Mechanism `ACTIVE->DEPRECATED`.
  Receptor cascade step 2: Object ABANDONED Ôłë
  {ACTIVE,SUSPENDED,DEPRECATED} Ôćĺ fails.
  **BLOCKED**: Mechanism `ACTIVE->DEPRECATED` MUST be
  rejected (composition ÔÇö on failure: reject source).

  ====

  **┬ž12 ÔÇö Restoration path**

  SC-100 ÔÇö Structure(ACTIVE), Mechanism(SUSPENDED).
  Mechanism `SUSPENDED->ACTIVE`.
  **PASS**: ACTIVE Ôłł {ACTIVE,DEPRECATED}.

  SC-101 ÔÇö Structure(SUSPENDED), Mechanism(SUSPENDED).
  Mechanism `SUSPENDED->ACTIVE`.
  **BLOCKED**: SUSPENDED Ôłë {ACTIVE,DEPRECATED}.

  SC-102 ÔÇö Structure(DEPRECATED), Mechanism(DEPRECATED).
  Mechanism `DEPRECATED->SUSPENDED`.
  **PASS**: DEPRECATED Ôłł {ACTIVE,SUSPENDED,DEPRECATED}.

  SC-103 ÔÇö Structure(ACTIVE), Mechanism(SUSPENDED),
  Effector(SUSPENDED), Receptor(SUSPENDED).
  Effector.Object(ACTIVE), Receptor.Object(ACTIVE).
  Mechanism `SUSPENDED->ACTIVE`.
  **CASCADE** (composition): Effector `SUSPENDED->ACTIVE`
  (step 2 OK: Object ACTIVE Ôłł {ACTIVE,DEPRECATED}),
  Receptor `SUSPENDED->ACTIVE` (same).
  No reference cascade (restoration not in scope).
